product.name: RainBowl Chia Pudding
product.description: This Rainbowl Chia Pudding not only satisfies a sweet tooth, but it is full of healthy antioxidant-rich foods. Chia is an increasingly popular food ingredient among consumers and manufacturers. The nutrient-rich seeds are good sources of α-linolenic acid (an omega-3 fatty acid), fiber, protein, vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, prompting claims that chia is “superfood.

product.name: Feel Good Overnight Oatmeal
product.description: Overnight oats are simply oats that are left to soak overnight instead of cooked in the morning, which makes them perfect for a quick, filling and nutritious breakfast. It's a bit like making cold-brew coffee instead of the regular cup of hot coffee in the morning. Our overnight oatmeals are also some of our favorite desserts. They are creamy, dreamy, and delicious.

product.name: Soup season is back
product.description: When there's just too much on your mind, that's when the warm, uncomplicated goodness of soup hits the spot.
